<topic id="how-to-ibm-db2">
  <title>Configuring an IBM DB2 Database Connection</title>
  <body>
    <p>To configure the support for the IBM DB2 database, follow this procedure:<ol>
        <li><ph conkeyref="reusables-configuring-oxygen/ibm_db2_driver_download"/></li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-db2-datasource.dita#configure-db2-datasource">Configure
            IBM DB2 <term>Data Source</term> drivers</xref>.</li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-db2-connection.dita#configure-db2-connection">Configure
            an IBM DB2 Server <term>Connection</term></xref>.</li>
        <li>To view your connection, go to the <xref
            href="../topics/relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"
              ><uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>
          <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view-parenthesis"/> or switch to the
            <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
          <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref>.</li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
